ALC_Reasoner

Class ChronologicalTableau

  • java.lang.Object
    • ALC_Reasoner.ChronologicalTableau
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Tableau

    public class ChronologicalTableau
extends java.lang.Object
implements Tableau
    Chronological ALC_Reasoner.Tableau is a class that implements the ALC_Reasoner.Tableau interface. The reasoning technique is the basic one, in particular during the backtrack phase we always return to the last concept that generated a branch.

      • someRelation

        private final java.util.Map<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLObjectPropertyExpression,java.util.List<java.lang.Integer>> someRelation
        The Some relation. A map that keeps track of existential quantifiers encountered during reasoning. The keySet is of type OWLObjectPropertyExpression, the valueSet is a list of integers. So passing the relationship type this object return a list of pointers to the conceptList.

      • allRelation

        private final java.util.Map<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLObjectPropertyExpression,java.util.List<java.lang.Integer>> allRelation
        The All relation. A map that keeps track of universal quantifiers encountered during reasoning. The keySet is of type OWLObjectPropertyExpression, the valueSet is a list of integers. So passing the relationship type this object return a list of pointers to the conceptList.

      • iteration

        private int iteration
        The Iterations. An int variable that acts as a counter for the number of iterations needed to complete the reasoning.

      • conceptComparator

        private final java.util.Comparator<? super org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLClassExpression> conceptComparator
        The Concept comparator. It is an object used to reorder objects of type OWLClassExpression. The order relation is as follows: "OBJECT_INTERSECTION_OF < OBJECT_UNION_OF < OBJECT_SOME_VALUES_FROM < OBJECT_ALL_VALUES_FROM < OBJECT_COMPLEMENT_OF <= OWL_CLASS"
